{"tid":28944,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[高登神戲] 無間道算唔算有bug","createTime":"2016-12-08T09:06:17.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-08T10:11:00.000Z","uid":30049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"706a4558a8f6ad83c888dce8360f683bad58ec44","tid":28944,"uid":30049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T09:06:17.000Z","msg":"最後林家棟上天台救左劉德華<br />\n話自己都係韓琛既人 只係冇被發掘<br />\n姐係話林係識劉 劉(應該)唔識林<br />\n<br />\n但問題就黎啦<br />\n一開始劉扮律師審犯攞料<br />\n其間有運用到係韓琛果邊既料 (知道某啲名)<br />\n但就唔覺意比林係cctv聽到<br />\n出黎果陣林又問番劉 點解知果啲名<br />\n搞到劉一時唔識答 (唔知比人偷聽到)<br />\n<br />\n咁點解林明知劉係同伴 都要突登問好似玩鳩佢咁？ 路驚比人聽到？<br />\n定係為左鋪路話比觀眾聽林都係鬼？ <br />\n<br />\n雖然唔算好影響故事<br />\n但睇左幾次都係覺得怪怪地<br />\n有冇人講解下"},{"pid":"94638e1fb07593dc991c200c106fb37fcdc567d9","tid":28944,"uid":30049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T09:07:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41ef3d7cdabbd4a1e5905cddac2e06200dee28bd","tid":28944,"uid":30049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T09:07:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39d5f852a6d27c6f38c9a04a1e59231323071f01","tid":28944,"uid":30049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T09:07:57.000Z","msg":"3<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"650f6aa137cbcf897778937818d44e1418bbdb13","tid":28944,"uid":30049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T09:08:08.000Z","msg":"4<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1225410ffab4d8500192613dc2a1267401fdbe3b","tid":28944,"uid":30049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T09:08:20.000Z","msg":"5<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44743e9b88653ea1992f18cfc4a1d789ce74fc9c","tid":28944,"uid":30049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T09:0